<collectingMunicipality id="6B86ACEDFFB2F845FE8224E6FE63FD6C" box="[348,398,727,753]" pageId="3" pageNumber="438">This</collectingMunicipality>
species was described from “Brasilia; ad Serra da Lapa in provincial 
<collectingRegion id="4999F875FFB2F845FB1824E6FAB2FD6C" box="[1222,1375,727,753]" country="Brazil" name="Minas Gerais" pageId="3" pageNumber="438">Minas Geraïs</collectingRegion>
a 
<collectorName id="26A85341FFB2F845FA5F24E6FEEAFC88" pageId="3" pageNumber="438">D. Ménétriés</collectorName>
detecta.”. 
<location id="8E82604CFFB2F845FEA024CAFE47FC88" LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:03F48781FFB2F845FF4927CFFE99FC1C:8E82604CFFB2F845FEA024CAFE47FC88" box="[382,426,763,789]" municipality="This" name="The" pageId="3" pageNumber="438" stateProvince="Minas Gerais">The</location>
<typeStatus id="54E68835FFB2F845FE6F24CAFDF5FC88" box="[433,536,763,789]" pageId="3" pageNumber="438">lectotype</typeStatus>
housed at the 
<collectionCode id="ED4CAE52FFB2F845FD6724CAFCEAFC88" box="[697,775,763,789]" pageId="3" pageNumber="438">MZHF</collectionCode>
is labelled as “Brasilia Min. Geraës” (
<collectorName id="26A85341FFB2F845FB6B24CAFACAFC88" box="[1205,1319,763,789]" pageId="3" pageNumber="438">Ménétriés</collectorName>
leg.).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BE23697FFB2F845FF19252EFE99FC1C" blockId="3.[151,1437,510,897]" pageId="3" pageNumber="438">
This species was erroneously listed within the subgenus 
<taxonomicName id="4C5D4D14FFB2F845FC9B252EFC15FCA4" authorityName="Bellamy &amp; Westcott" authorityYear="2000" box="[837,1016,799,825]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Hyperanthoides" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="438" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B929EA85FFB2F845FC9B252EFC15FCA4" box="[837,1016,799,825]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="438">Hyperanthoides</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
of the genus 
<taxonomicName id="4C5D4D14FFB2F845FB4F252EFAFFFCA4" authorityName="Gistel" authorityYear="1834" box="[1169,1298,799,825]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Hiperantha" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="438" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B929EA85FFB2F845FB4F252EFAFFFCA4" box="[1169,1298,799,825]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="438">Hiperantha</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by 
<bibRefCitation id="EFCC4B66FFB2F845FAE3252EFE84FCC0" author="Bellamy &amp; Westcott" firstAuthor="Bellamy" pageId="3" pageNumber="438" pagination="25 - 34" refId="ref2148" refString="Bellamy, C. L. &amp; Westcott, R. L. (2000) The genus Hiperantha: subgenera, type species, unavailable names and the Mexican fauna (Coleoptera: Buprestidae). Folia Heyrovskyana, 8 (1), 25 - 34." type="journal article" year="2000">Bellamy &amp; Westcott (2000)</bibRefCitation>
, but 
<bibRefCitation id="EFCC4B66FFB2F845FE412572FDA2FCC0" author="Bellamy" box="[415,591,835,861]" firstAuthor="Bellamy" pageId="3" pageNumber="438" pagination="626 - 1260" refId="ref2197" refString="Bellamy, C. L. (2008) s. n. In: A World Catalogue and Bibliography of the Jewel Beetles (Coleoptera: Buprestoidea). Vol. 2. Chrysochroinae: Sphenopterini through Buprestinae: Stigmoderini. Pensoft Series Faunistica No. 77. Pensoft Publishers, Sofia Moscow, pp. 626 - 1260." type="book chapter" year="2008">Bellamy (2008)</bibRefCitation>
placed it into the correct subgenus as 
<taxonomicName id="4C5D4D14FFB2F845FC242572FE82FC1C" authority="Mannerheim, 1837" authorityName="Mannerheim" authorityYear="1837" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Hiperantha" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="438" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="sanguinosa" subGenus="Hiperantha">
<emphasis id="B929EA85FFB2F845FC242572FB96FCC0" box="[1018,1147,835,861]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="438">Hiperantha</emphasis>
(
<emphasis id="B929EA85FFB2F845FB552572FAE1FCC0" box="[1163,1292,835,861]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="438">Hiperantha</emphasis>
) 
<emphasis id="B929EA85FFB2F845FAC32572FA70FCC1" box="[1309,1437,835,860]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="438">sanguinosa</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFCC4B66FFB2F845FF492556FE82FC1C" author="Mannerheim" box="[151,367,871,897]" firstAuthor="Mannerheim" pageId="3" pageNumber="438" pagination="1 - 126" refId="ref2290" refString="Mannerheim, C. G. von (1837) Enumeration des Buprestides, et description de quelques nouvelles especes de cette tribu de la famille des Sternoxes, de la collection de M. Le Comte Mannerheim. Bulletin de la Societe Imperiale des Naturalistes des Moscou, 8, 1 - 126." type="journal article" year="1837">Mannerheim, 1837</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
